      "utilityType": "other",
      "description": "Give one visible creature within 60 feet that can understand you a verbal command to perform a service or avoid an activity for 30 days. On a failed Wisdom save, the target is Charmed, takes 5d10 Psychic damage no more than once each day when it acts directly against the command, ends the spell if given a suicidal command, can be freed by Remove Curse, Greater Restoration, or Wish, and higher slots extend the duration to 365 days at slots 7-8 or until ended at slot 9.",
